thread.title: David Wiltshire

author: David Wiltshire
title: David Wiltshire
text: My experience with Storage mart has been a good one to date. The Ladies over at the Tretheway Location as absolutely charming. Jazz handled my request with professionalism and charisma. the manager (Cheryl) is a good laugh but all in a respectable manner. So far all my storage needs have been met and i look forward to doing further business with them in the near future.
